  "body": "<p>Here's a continuation (at long last!) from <a href=\"https://www.amytangerine.com/blog/2012/09/australia-wrap-up\">this Spotlight wrap up post</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"3a-IMG_0778-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/08c3a783c93d5fd1.jpg?v=1782537491\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"3b-IMG_0771-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/79c18f43c0c0c3bc.jpg?v=1782537494\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3c-IMG_0787-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/27d3e864ce20cb48.jpg?v=1782537496\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3d-IMG_0795-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/621c15597b4015f1.jpg?v=1782537499\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3e-IMG_0801-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c620ad0cb0175164.jpg?v=1782537502\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3f-IMG_0813-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/15dae8abe0d90751.jpg?v=1782537505\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3g-IMG_0820-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/811ad6292f456f8d.jpg?v=1782537508\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3h-IMG_0830-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/45076ea1cd858db4.jpg?v=1782537510\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3i-IMG_0826-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/eb2bfb3b4aa10227.jpg?v=1782537514\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3j-IMG_0836-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a22b382fadeedfea.jpg?v=1782537516\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3k-IMG_0822-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/bbab3d98c67d867c.jpg?v=1782537519\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Still love how Beth immediately documented the visit in her Project Life. Other bloggers include <a href=\"http://btsoi.blogspot.com/2012/08/meeting-amy-tan.html\">btsoi</a> and <a href=\"http://intheeyesofmoonie.blogspot.com.au/2012/09/amy-tan-in-caboolture.html\">Moonie</a> and <a href=\"http://captureandcreate.wordpress.com/2012/09/09/helloooooo-anyone-there/\">Mandy B</a>. There's nothing quite like meeting all these wonderful, creative folks in person. Thanks again American Crafts, Spotlight and everyone who was a part of this awesome experience! Truly blessed and grateful.</p>"
